src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Numbers Midday' game
03 Nov 2019, 18:40 by The Associated Press
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday afternoon's drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery's "Numbers Midday" game were:
4-9-5-4
(four, nine, five, four)
